Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:14.98,ED日文,,0000,0000,0000,,All the school kids so sick of books\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:16.98,ED日文,,0000,0000,0000,,They like the punk and the metal band\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.22,0:23:19.52,ED日文,,0000,0000,0000,,When the buzzer rings(oh whey oh)\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.52,0:23:21.90,ED日文,,0000,0000,0000,,They're walking like an Egyptian\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:24.00,ED日文,,0000,0000,0000,,All the kids in the marketplace say\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:26.60,ED日文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ay oh whey oh  \N
